#note: cf. 6.1.15.c15

1.B.11. [geme₂ niŋ₂ hi-li]-a#-ke₄# {d}iškur diŋir lugal LIL₂!-e
#lem: geme[female worker]; niŋ[thing]; hili[attractiveness]; Iškur[1]DN; diŋir[deity]; lugal[king]; X
#etcsl: line-id=1.B.11

#note: cf. 6.1.03.36, 6.2.3: UET 6/2 325 ll. 3-5

1.B.12. [ukuš₂-gin₇ ki dug₃] hu#-mu-dar#-e-še
